com.inqwell.any.ref

Class AnyReferenceQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.ref.ReferenceQueue
      • com.inqwell.any.ref.AnyReferenceQueue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Any, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SweptReferenceQueue

    public class AnyReferenceQueue
extends ReferenceQueue
implements Any
    Extends the standard JDK ReferenceQueue class to make it a collectable Any and to return enqueued reference objects as AnySoftReference instances.
